'''Derek Lyons''' (born [[September 25]], [[1950s#1958|1958]]) portrayed a [[Rebel Honor Guard|Massassi Temple Guard]], as well as the [[Medal of Bravery|medal]] bearer later [[Retroactive continuity|retconned]] as [[Voren Na'al]], in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].

